---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Home"
  description="MiMaji Foundation is solving the water crisis across East Africa and beyond. We provide clean, safe water access to underserved communities in Kenya, Uganda, Ethiopia, Somalia, Rwanda, Burundi, and Tanzania."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge"><span class="pulse"></span> Phase 1: Pilot Programme &mdash; Nairobi, Kenya</div>
      <h1>Clean Water Is a Right,<br>Not a <em>Privilege</em></h1>
      <p>MiMaji Foundation is a small, dedicated team building toward a future where every community has reliable access to safe, affordable water. We are starting where we live and where we know the problem deepest: Nairobi.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/the-problem/" class="btn btn-primary">Understand the Crisis &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline">Our Mission</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">400M+</span><span class="label">People Without Safe Water in Sub-Saharan Africa</span></div>
        <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">10x</span><span class="label">Price Gap Between Kibera & Karen for Water</span></div>
        <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">2025</span><span class="label">Year Founded</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- CRISIS -->
  <section class="bg-sand" id="crisis">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">The Water Crisis</div>
      <div class="section-title">Africa Carries the World's Heaviest Water Burden</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">While water scarcity is a global challenge, Sub-Saharan Africa faces the deepest and most urgent crisis. These are the facts driving our work.</div>
      <div class="crisis-grid fade-in">
        <div class="crisis-visual">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594398901394-4e34b2348fb0?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Children collecting water in East Africa" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="overlay">
            <p>Every day, millions of children walk hours to collect water instead of attending school.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="crisis-facts">
          <div class="crisis-fact">
            <div class="icon">💧</div>
            <div>
              <h4>400 Million People Lack Safe Water</h4>
              <p>Sub-Saharan Africa is home to the vast majority of the world's water-insecure population. Access rates remain the lowest of any global region.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="crisis-fact">
            <div class="icon">🚶</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Women Walk 6+ Hours Daily</h4>
              <p>In rural East Africa, women and girls bear the burden of water collection — often walking over 6 kilometres each day, sacrificing education and economic opportunity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="crisis-fact">
            <div class="icon">⚠️</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Waterborne Diseases Kill Thousands</h4>
              <p>Contaminated water causes cholera, typhoid, and diarrheal diseases that disproportionately kill children under 5 across the continent.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="crisis-fact">
            <div class="icon">📉</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Economic Growth Held Back</h4>
              <p>The African Development Bank estimates water insecurity costs African economies billions annually in lost productivity, healthcare costs, and stunted human capital.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section id="mission">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Our Mission</div>
      <div class="section-title">Technology-Driven Water Access at Scale</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">We combine local community knowledge with modern technology to create sustainable water solutions that last generations.</div>
      <div class="mission-cards">
        <div class="mission-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">🔬</div>
          <h3>Water Quality Testing</h3>
          <p>We bring free water quality testing to underserved communities, using TDS meters and bacteriological test kits to identify contamination and educate residents on safe water practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">🌍</div>
          <h3>Community Education</h3>
          <p>Through workshops, schools, and community health workers, we teach safe water storage, treatment, and hygiene — empowering communities to protect their own health.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">📱</div>
          <h3>Platform-Powered Delivery</h3>
          <p>Backed by the <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600;">MiMaji technology platform</a>, we connect communities to verified clean water sources and affordable delivery — making safe water accessible on demand.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOCUS COUNTRIES -->
  <section class="focus-section" id="focus">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Where We Work</div>
      <div class="section-title">Starting in East Africa, Scaling to the World</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">We focus where the need is greatest. East Africa is our launchpad — but our vision is global.</div>
      <div class="focus-grid">
        <div class="country-list fade-in">
          <div class="country-item active">
            <span class="flag">🇰🇪</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Kenya</h4><p>Phase 1 &bull; Pilot Active</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇺🇬</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Uganda</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇪🇹</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Ethiopia</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇸🇴</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Somalia</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇷🇼</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Rwanda</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇧🇮</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Burundi</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇹🇿</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Tanzania</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-map fade-in">
          <div class="map-placeholder">
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="map-text">
              <span class="big">1</span>
              <span class="sub">Active &bull; 6 in our regional vision</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHERE WE ARE -->
  <section class="bg-sand" id="where-we-are">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Where We Are</div>
      <div class="section-title">Honest About Our Stage</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">We are a small team in the pilot phase. We don&rsquo;t have inflated impact numbers to share &mdash; not yet. What we have is a clear plan, real research, and a commitment to building this the right way.</div>
      <div class="stage-grid fade-in">
        <div class="stage-card">
          <div class="stage-tag">Now</div>
          <h4>Pilot Phase</h4>
          <p>Building the team, finalising water quality testing protocols, and preparing the first community testing events in Nairobi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <div class="stage-tag">Next</div>
          <h4>MajiMap Launch</h4>
          <p>Phase 1 of <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> &mdash; turning the Nairobi water price research into a public, interactive data tool.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <div class="stage-tag">Soon</div>
          <h4>Schools Programme</h4>
          <p>Launching <a href="/water-in-schools/">water quality testing in Nairobi schools</a> with student ambassador training.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-card">
          <div class="stage-tag">Vision</div>
          <h4>Regional Expansion</h4>
          <p>Expanding water access programmes across East Africa as we build capacity, partnerships, and proven impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">The Water Crisis Won't Solve Itself.<br>But Together, We Can.</div>
    <p>Whether you're a partner, donor, volunteer, or community leader — there's a role for you in the MiMaji mission. Let's build a future where clean water is a given, not a luxury.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-white">Visit MiMaji Platform &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Get In Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, var(--blue-deep) 0%, var(--blue) 40%, var(--sky) 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Ccircle cx='30' cy='30' r='2'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  .hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 880px;
    padding: 2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    padding: 0.45rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .pulse {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-stat .num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--white);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-stat .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-stats {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* Stage cards */
  .stage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .stage-card {
    padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .stage-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .stage-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: rgba(244, 169, 48, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .stage-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stage-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stage-card a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .stage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .stage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
